  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

<p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> June 11, 2026</p>

<p>
    Thank you for using our app ("the App"). This Privacy Policy explains how we collect,
    use, disclose, and protect information when you use the App.
</p>

<p>
    By using the App, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance
    with this Privacy Policy.
</p>

<h2>Information We Collect</h2>

<p>Depending on the features you use, the App may collect or process the following information:</p>

<h3>Information You Provide</h3>
<ul>
    <li>Account information (if account creation or sign-in is supported)</li>
    <li>Feedback, support requests, or communications you send to us</li>
    <li>Content you voluntarily submit through the App</li>
</ul>

<h3>Automatically Collected Information</h3>
<p>The App and its service providers may automatically collect:</p>

<ul>
    <li>Device information (device model, operating system version, language settings)</li>
    <li>App usage information</li>
    <li>Crash reports and diagnostic information</li>
    <li>IP address and general location information</li>
    <li>Advertising or analytics identifiers, where applicable</li>
</ul>

<h2>Third-Party Services</h2>

<p>
    The App may use third-party services that collect information in accordance with
    their own privacy policies.
</p>

<p>These services may include:</p>

<h3>Google Play Services</h3>

<p>Google Play Services may be used for:</p>

<ul>
    <li>Authentication and sign-in</li>
    <li>Analytics</li>
    <li>In-app purchases</li>
    <li>Device and service functionality required by Android</li>
</ul>

<p>
    Google's Privacy Policy:
    <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        https://policies.google.com/privacy
    </a>
</p>

<h3>Google Play Games Services</h3>

<p>The App may use Google Play Games Services to provide:</p>

<ul>
    <li>Player sign-in</li>
    <li>Leaderboards</li>
    <li>Achievements</li>
    <li>Saved game functionality (if enabled)</li>
    <li>Other Play Games features</li>
</ul>

<p>
    When these features are used, Google may process information such as:
</p>

<ul>
    <li>Google Play Games Player ID</li>
    <li>Profile name</li>
    <li>Achievement progress</li>
    <li>Leaderboard scores</li>
    <li>Saved game data</li>
    <li>Related gameplay information required to provide Play Games Services</li>
</ul>

<p>
    This information is processed by Google according to Google's privacy practices.
</p>

<p>
    Google Privacy Policy:
    <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        https://policies.google.com/privacy
    </a>
</p>

<h2>How We Use Information</h2>

<p>We may use collected information to:</p>

<ul>
    <li>Provide and maintain the App</li>
    <li>Improve functionality and performance</li>
    <li>Monitor usage and diagnose technical issues</li>
    <li>Process purchases and transactions</li>
    <li>Enable online features such as leaderboards and achievements</li>
    <li>Respond to support requests</li>
    <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
</ul>

<h2>Data Sharing</h2>

<p>We do not sell personal information.</p>

<p>Information may be shared only:</p>

<ul>
    <li>With service providers that help operate the App</li>
    <li>With platform providers such as Google when required for functionality</li>
    <li>To comply with legal obligations</li>
    <li>To protect our rights, users, or the public</li>
    <li>In connection with a business transfer, merger, or acquisition</li>
</ul>

<h2>Data Retention</h2>

<p>We retain information only for as long as necessary to:</p>

<ul>
    <li>Provide the App's services</li>
    <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
    <li>Resolve disputes</li>
    <li>Enforce agreements</li>
</ul>

<p>
    Retention periods may vary depending on the type of information and applicable laws.
</p>

<h2>Children's Privacy</h2>

<p>
    The App is not intended for children under 13 unless explicitly stated otherwise.
</p>

<p>
    We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.
    If you believe a child has provided personal information, please contact us
